28 September 2008Members of the media are advised that President Kgalema Motlanthe will, for the first time as President of the Republic, address the nation in a televised address on SABC 2.The address will take place as follows:Date Sunday, 28 September 2008 Time 19:00 TV station /channel SABC 2Enquiries Harold Maloka Cell: 082 847 9799Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)